title: Didnt get the new poro icon
body: I did everything that was necessary to get it but i still haven't gotten it yet, is this only for me?

replies.body: It's not only you, there are a lot of accounts to gift and they are being sent out separately.  Per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-), it's going to take some more time to gift everyone.  Hang tight!
